sql.up: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS "user"  (id uuid   primary key   default (gen_random_uuid () )  not null  , username varchar (2048)  not null  , "hashedPassword" varchar (2048)  not null  , "twoFactorSecret" varchar (2048) , role role []  default ((ARRAY[('user')])::role [])  not null  , CONSTRAINT user_username_unique  unique (username)  )
